comment:
* Keys for {@link HealthStats} returned from
 * {@link HealthStats#getStats(int) HealthStats.getStats(int)} with the
 * {@link UidHealthStats#STATS_PROCESSES UidHealthStats.STATS_PROCESSES} key.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_USER_TIME_MS
variables.comment:
* Key for a measurement of number of millseconds the CPU spent running in user space
     * for this process.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_SYSTEM_TIME_MS
variables.comment:
* Key for a measurement of number of millseconds the CPU spent running in kernel space
     * for this process.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_STARTS_COUNT
variables.comment: * Key for a measurement of the number of times this process was started for any reason.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_CRASHES_COUNT
variables.comment: * Key for a measurement of the number of crashes that happened in this process.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_ANR_COUNT
variables.comment: * Key for a measurement of the number of ANRs that happened in this process.

variables.name: MEASUREMENT_FOREGROUND_MS
variables.comment:
* Key for a measurement of the number of milliseconds this process spent with
     * an activity in the foreground.
